观看 Talking Heads 在“危险边缘！”中展示他们自己的类别https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-talking-heads-present-their-own-category-on-jeopardy-3803302?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-talking-heads-present-their-自身类别处于危险之中Liberty DunworthWed, 16 Oct 2024 10:44:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3803302 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="会说话的头像出现在美国电视上" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>问题围绕着他们的唱片和音乐会电影“Stop Making Sense”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-talking-heads-present-their-own-category-on-jeopardy-3803302">Watch Talking Heads 发布了他们自己的“危险边缘！”类别</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="会说话的头像出现在美国电视上" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Talking-heads@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>会<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heads">说话的头像</a>出现在美国游戏节目<em>《危险边缘》中！</em> ，并提出了自己类别中的问题。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/talking-heads-every-album-ranked-in-order-of-greatness-3486762"><b>Talking Heads：每张专辑按伟大程度排列</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这部长期播出的游戏节目系列的这一集于昨晚（10 月 15 日）播出，标志性乐队出现在该集的一部分中，在特殊的 Talking Heads 类别中提出问题。</p><p>在该系列和乐队在社交媒体上分享的这段视频中，四人首先介绍了自己，然后向参赛者提出了有关他们的唱片和音乐会电影<em>《Stop Making Sense》</em>的问题。</p><p>乐队最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/talking-heads-stop-making-sense-documentary-is-returning-to-cinemas-after-39-years-3414795">通过 A24 分享了重新发行的音乐会电影 40 周年</a>。随后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-announce-return-with-cover-on-talking-heads-tribute-album-3568542">五月推出了一张致敬专辑</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a>等艺术家都翻唱了乐队最著名的曲目。</p><p> “除此之外，我们是<em>《别再胡言乱语</em>》的明星了，”大卫·布莱恩在视频开头说道，克里斯·弗兰茨补充道：“被誉为有史以来最伟大的音乐会电影”。</p><p> “现在它要在 40 周年纪念日重新上映了，”蒂娜·韦茅斯继续说道，而杰里·哈里森则说道：“我们将获得有关这部电影和我们音乐的线索。”</p><p>在该片段中，会员们询问了有关他们最热门影片的问题，包括《精神病杀手》和《烧毁房子》，以及更一般性的问题，比如谁执导了《 <em>Stop Making Sense》</em>电影以及哪个标志性的纽约俱乐部观看了这些影片播放他们的第一场演出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DBKjc3KyA1V/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; bord